WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.250 --> 01:43.981
=Episode 17=

02:06.608 --> 02:07.168
Sir,

02:07.367 --> 02:09.448
will these steel bars be okay under...

02:12.687 --> 02:13.247
Sir,

02:13.448 --> 02:15.647
will these steel bars be okay
under the sun?

02:19.664 --> 02:21.609
â™ªWhere does the soul come fromâ™ª

02:21.609 --> 02:23.422
â™ªAn island of exile for dreamsâ™ª

02:23.422 --> 02:25.397
â™ªTempered by critiquesâ™ª

02:25.397 --> 02:27.195
â™ªEyes shining brighterâ™ª

02:27.195 --> 02:29.229
â™ªButterfly breaking free in the mirrorâ™ª

02:29.229 --> 02:31.217
â™ªPerfect, for no oneâ™ª

02:32.247 --> 02:32.647
Alright.

02:32.687 --> 02:34.087
Check this out, everyone.

02:34.087 --> 02:36.328
The Barbie pants I'm holding
come with the belt design.

02:36.408 --> 02:37.207
They're in Link 1.

02:37.367 --> 02:38.888
And our host, Yan,

02:39.048 --> 02:40.647
is wearing the pair available in Link 2.

02:40.728 --> 02:42.087
Order according to your needs.

02:42.527 --> 02:44.848
These Barbie pants
truly contour your figure,

02:44.927 --> 02:45.848
provide real warmth,

02:46.008 --> 02:49.128
and most importantly,
have exceptional stretchiness.

02:49.128 --> 02:49.927
Let's demonstrate.

02:54.967 --> 02:55.807
Dear viewers,

02:55.807 --> 02:57.168
look at what Yan is holding.

02:57.288 --> 02:58.807
These are expired instant noodles,

02:58.967 --> 03:00.008
expired coffee,

03:00.008 --> 03:01.207
and some stubborn stains

03:01.207 --> 03:02.647
like expired milk.

03:02.807 --> 03:03.728
To clean them,

03:03.767 --> 03:05.728
we'd need to sweep first
and then mop, right?

03:05.927 --> 03:06.967
But today is different

03:07.247 --> 03:10.008
because we have this high-end
intelligent floor washer.

03:10.527 --> 03:12.728
Effortlessly, without manual work,

03:12.888 --> 03:16.128
we achieve perfect cleanliness.

03:16.288 --> 03:17.247
Ready?

03:17.568 --> 03:18.367
Let's go.

03:18.848 --> 03:19.767
Three.

03:20.888 --> 03:21.568
Did you see?

03:21.767 --> 03:22.568
Did you see?

03:22.568 --> 03:23.207
The noodles

03:23.207 --> 03:24.288
get completely vacuumed.

03:24.687 --> 03:26.168
Then let's pull it back

03:26.448 --> 03:27.568
and wipe casually.

03:27.647 --> 03:29.128
Spotless!

03:29.168 --> 03:30.527
And it's effortless.

03:30.527 --> 03:32.128
You can do it single-handedly.

03:32.128 --> 03:32.608
Exactly.

03:32.608 --> 03:33.687
It's power assisted.

03:33.687 --> 03:34.168
Right.

03:34.168 --> 03:36.608
And it's not a noisy machine.

03:36.888 --> 03:37.848
This price drop

03:37.848 --> 03:39.207
is a limited chance. Grab it.

03:41.573 --> 03:45.360
â™ªMy beauty's defined by none
but my own commandâ™ª

03:47.207 --> 03:48.487
Clean as new.

03:48.944 --> 03:51.330
â™ªLike a raw diamondâ™ª

03:51.967 --> 03:53.967
Next, let's check

03:53.967 --> 03:55.328
the cleaning performance.

03:55.448 --> 03:56.288
It's self-cleaning.

03:56.408 --> 03:57.367
Let's test it

03:57.367 --> 03:58.728
on the table for our viewers.

03:59.087 --> 03:59.807
It's light.

03:59.807 --> 04:01.128
So no issues at all.

04:02.927 --> 04:03.767
Check your phone.

04:03.767 --> 04:04.888
It's available in Link 1.

04:06.048 --> 04:06.848
It's furry.

04:07.888 --> 04:08.656
It's on her face.

04:09.888 --> 04:11.247
Know what this means?

04:11.328 --> 04:12.168
It's truly clean.

04:14.636 --> 04:16.351
â™ªReady to shineâ™ª

04:16.807 --> 04:17.608
Mr. He.

04:18.768 --> 04:19.807
Here. Good work.

04:21.088 --> 04:21.768
Mr. Li.

04:25.927 --> 04:26.687
Good work.

04:26.687 --> 04:27.408
Thanks.

04:29.367 --> 04:31.768
I've noticed these steel bars
sitting here for days.

04:31.768 --> 04:32.408
Is it okay?

04:32.487 --> 04:33.367
How is it okay?

04:33.927 --> 04:35.807
When it rains

04:35.887 --> 04:37.088
and then the sun bakes them,

04:37.288 --> 04:38.807
they'll completely rust.

04:39.127 --> 04:40.687
They'll rust overnight,

04:40.687 --> 04:41.608
totally oxidized.

04:41.728 --> 04:43.247
So these bars will oxidize?

04:43.648 --> 04:44.127
Exactly.

04:44.168 --> 04:45.528
Look at that building.

04:45.648 --> 04:46.728
No protection at all.

04:46.768 --> 04:47.887
When rain gets inside,

04:47.887 --> 04:49.768
all the steel bars rust.

04:49.927 --> 04:51.247
So there's lots of steel inside?

04:51.288 --> 04:51.807
Right.

04:51.848 --> 04:52.687
It's all good steel.

04:52.687 --> 04:54.048
Now it's all wasted?

04:54.208 --> 04:55.327
Rust makes them unusable.

04:55.327 --> 04:56.240
And what about those?

04:56.528 --> 04:57.528
Can't use them, either.

04:58.168 --> 04:58.728
Got it.

04:59.927 --> 05:01.007
Everyone, speed up.

05:01.048 --> 05:01.648
Over here.

05:01.648 --> 05:02.327
Move faster.

05:02.807 --> 05:03.768
Hurry up!

05:03.848 --> 05:04.447
Look.

05:04.648 --> 05:05.728
Didn't you hear Mr. Zhang?

05:05.728 --> 05:06.247
Faster!

05:06.327 --> 05:06.968
Look.

05:08.048 --> 05:09.567
How lazy everyone's become!

05:10.687 --> 05:11.807
Listen up!

05:14.088 --> 05:16.247
We're gathered here today

05:16.247 --> 05:17.168
for two matters.

05:17.528 --> 05:18.088
First,

05:18.247 --> 05:20.432
allow me to formally introduce

05:21.397 --> 05:25.088
Mr. Shen, who was dispatched
by the group's headquarters.

05:25.487 --> 05:26.367
Let's welcome him.

05:30.408 --> 05:30.968
Alright.

05:31.447 --> 05:32.447
Second,

05:33.048 --> 05:36.768
Mr. Shen has some instructions
for everyone.

05:37.367 --> 05:37.968
Please.

05:40.088 --> 05:42.007
I'll skip the formalities.

05:42.968 --> 05:44.168
My purpose here

05:45.048 --> 05:48.208
is to investigate the project delays.

05:51.848 --> 05:53.408
Of course there are issues.

05:54.327 --> 05:56.848
All the problems
are laid out plain as day.

05:57.528 --> 05:59.848
Investor Mr. Wu ran off with the money

06:00.088 --> 06:03.048
and wronged all my workers, right?

06:03.048 --> 06:03.487
Right.

06:03.487 --> 06:04.807
Funds were depleted after he ran.

06:04.807 --> 06:05.608
Right?

06:05.648 --> 06:06.088
Right.

06:06.168 --> 06:07.168
As for those funds...

06:07.807 --> 06:08.807
Quiet down! Quiet!

06:09.367 --> 06:10.768
Let Mr. Shen finish speaking.

06:12.887 --> 06:14.327
Regarding Wu Chengming's case,

06:14.528 --> 06:15.608
I'll handle it for sure.

06:16.288 --> 06:18.048
What I need to emphasize today is

06:18.927 --> 06:19.848
these days,

06:20.447 --> 06:21.528
I've discovered

06:21.608 --> 06:23.247
that at this site,

06:23.927 --> 06:26.088
major construction issues have surfaced.

06:26.807 --> 06:29.528
The steel reinforcement has been exposed
to the elements too long,

06:29.728 --> 06:30.648
causing oxidation.

06:31.927 --> 06:35.088
Delayed window installations

06:36.048 --> 06:38.032
left walls and ground waterlogged

06:38.448 --> 06:40.327
and all pipelines moldy.

06:41.088 --> 06:43.408
Missing wire mesh reinforcement

06:44.168 --> 06:45.327
has resulted in slab cracks.

06:46.567 --> 06:47.927
Due to these failures,

06:47.927 --> 06:49.288
immediate rectification and rework

06:49.327 --> 06:49.927
are required.

06:50.487 --> 06:52.048
Rework? With no pay?

06:52.927 --> 06:54.247
Show us the money first.

06:55.007 --> 06:56.007
Why is rework needed?

06:56.127 --> 06:57.887
Mr. Shen is demanding wildly.

06:58.327 --> 07:00.048
Even from your office,

07:00.288 --> 07:02.487
you know the construction site
inside and out.

07:04.048 --> 07:05.567
Did you hear him, department heads?

07:05.848 --> 07:06.848
Okay. Rework.

07:07.048 --> 07:08.367
You need money for that.

07:08.927 --> 07:09.608
Mr. Shen,

07:10.487 --> 07:12.168
the group has no allocated budget.

07:12.327 --> 07:14.247
What can we proceed

07:14.528 --> 07:15.408
and rework with?

07:15.447 --> 07:15.848
Right.

07:15.887 --> 07:16.327
Am I right?

07:16.367 --> 07:16.848
Exactly.

07:17.048 --> 07:17.848
There's no money.

07:18.168 --> 07:19.807
It's mainly about money.

07:19.968 --> 07:21.327
No money, no rework.

07:21.367 --> 07:21.807
Right.

07:21.848 --> 07:22.528
Right?

07:22.648 --> 07:23.768
Without money...

07:23.807 --> 07:25.127
Quiet! Quiet!

07:25.768 --> 07:26.807
Quiet! Quiet!

07:30.288 --> 07:31.367
Lost control, have we?

07:33.127 --> 07:33.768
Everyone,

07:33.968 --> 07:35.687
we've collaborated for years.

07:35.807 --> 07:37.088
Challenges exist,

07:37.247 --> 07:39.127
but Mr. Shen's new here.

07:39.367 --> 07:40.768
He needs time to understand.

07:40.848 --> 07:43.088
How about this? Do me a favor.

07:43.288 --> 07:43.807
Let's...

07:43.848 --> 07:48.048
We followed
the company's guidelines, right?

07:48.247 --> 07:50.757
Now you are accusing us
of non-compliance baselessly.

07:50.757 --> 07:51.728
That's not fair!

07:52.208 --> 07:53.048
That's not fair!

07:53.088 --> 07:53.528
Exactly!

07:53.567 --> 07:54.168
Right?

07:54.848 --> 07:57.288
Produce your individual contracts.

07:58.168 --> 08:00.288
We'll verify construction quality

08:00.487 --> 08:03.648
against initial specifications.

08:04.048 --> 08:06.968
No individual contracts.
We're just subcontractors.

08:07.807 --> 08:10.447
Then we'll sign
new individual contracts today.

08:11.447 --> 08:13.048
How to sign that?

08:13.408 --> 08:14.007
Exactly.

08:14.088 --> 08:17.447
The contracts specify
construction standards.

08:18.608 --> 08:23.367
(Labor Contract)
Compliant ones receive timely payments.

08:24.247 --> 08:26.648
Non-compliant work gets rectified

08:27.088 --> 08:29.968
with penalties for poor execution.

08:30.887 --> 08:32.648
All is clearly stipulated.

08:35.888 --> 08:36.727
Mr. Shen,

08:36.888 --> 08:38.447
this approach is unreasonable.

08:39.288 --> 08:42.368
I've managed projects for decades.

08:42.807 --> 08:44.768
These workers answer to me.

08:45.368 --> 08:47.847
We work under master contracts.
No individual contracts.

08:48.447 --> 08:50.168
You're breaking industry norms.

08:50.447 --> 08:51.847
It undermines my authority.

08:52.128 --> 08:53.248
No one will respect me.

08:53.368 --> 08:56.807
Our contracts
only govern construction standards

08:57.288 --> 08:58.447
and payment terms.

08:59.368 --> 09:01.048
No management authority is included.

09:01.727 --> 09:05.648
But from now on, all workers' salaries
won't go through your hands.

09:06.967 --> 09:12.048
And future financial audits
won't be a burden anymore.

09:12.727 --> 09:13.528
Isn't that good?

09:14.408 --> 09:15.168
Yes.

09:15.567 --> 09:16.648
It's great.

09:17.087 --> 09:18.408
It's great.

09:25.128 --> 09:27.128
- So much money?
- It's a lot!

09:29.207 --> 09:30.408
Starting today,

09:31.168 --> 09:34.368
report to my office
after work every day.

09:35.087 --> 09:36.768
Wages will be paid daily.

09:37.248 --> 09:38.087
Does your word count?

09:38.128 --> 09:39.528
Can we trust your word?

09:39.967 --> 09:40.768
Do you mean it?

09:40.847 --> 09:43.087
Those who agree can sign the contract.

09:43.528 --> 09:44.128
I'll sign it!

09:45.368 --> 09:46.168
No pushing.

09:46.727 --> 09:48.087
Stop shoving! Wait your turn.

09:48.087 --> 09:48.727
Mr. Shen,

09:49.128 --> 09:50.207
if you insist on this,

09:50.327 --> 09:51.768
we're walking out.

09:51.967 --> 09:53.168
We won't work today.

09:53.368 --> 09:54.008
Brothers,

09:54.288 --> 09:55.288
- let's go!
- Let's go!

09:55.288 --> 09:55.847
Let's go home.

09:56.008 --> 09:57.927
Li! Li, don't leave!

09:58.128 --> 09:59.087
Li, don't leave!

09:59.168 --> 09:59.727
Nobody leaves!

09:59.727 --> 10:00.368
I'm leaving.

10:00.368 --> 10:01.927
Mr. Shen, these are all key personnel.

10:02.048 --> 10:02.888
If they leave,

10:02.967 --> 10:04.288
the project will collapse.

10:04.327 --> 10:05.087
Move aside.

10:05.248 --> 10:06.008
Don't go.

10:08.288 --> 10:09.207
Hello, Mr. Zhang?

10:10.087 --> 10:11.248
Come report

10:11.528 --> 10:12.967
at 11 as agreed yesterday.

10:13.408 --> 10:14.087
Okay, Mr. Shen.

10:14.327 --> 10:15.927
I'll bring the whole tech team with me.

10:19.967 --> 10:20.648
Good.

10:21.408 --> 10:22.607
Don't regret this.

10:22.888 --> 10:23.488
Let's go!

10:23.967 --> 10:24.927
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

10:24.967 --> 10:25.687
Let's go.

10:25.687 --> 10:30.055
â™ªCause I just have been hurt
too many timesâ™ª

10:32.208 --> 10:35.008
â™ªI'm giving it all,
just getting nothing backâ™ª

10:35.008 --> 10:37.048
The money came at the perfect time.

10:40.327 --> 10:41.128
Sign here.

10:41.288 --> 10:41.847
Okay.

10:42.128 --> 10:42.648
Here?

10:42.807 --> 10:44.368
I'll keep this copy. You take that one.

10:44.488 --> 10:45.607
Great, thanks.

10:45.607 --> 10:47.207
Okay. This one's yours.

10:48.327 --> 10:49.128
Right, okay.

10:49.327 --> 10:49.847
Thanks.

10:49.847 --> 10:50.288
Sign here.

10:51.727 --> 10:52.128
Okay.

10:54.168 --> 10:54.807
Perfect.

10:55.248 --> 10:55.847
Sign here.

10:56.288 --> 10:57.567
(Labor Contract)
Sign your name here.

10:57.687 --> 10:58.207
Right.

10:59.168 --> 10:59.727
Here.

11:00.008 --> 11:00.447
Come on.

11:03.048 --> 11:05.048
Mr. Shen, you wanted to see me?

11:05.967 --> 11:06.248
Sit.

11:12.727 --> 11:14.048
Let's discuss

11:14.488 --> 11:16.648
the specifics of the project delays.

11:17.327 --> 11:18.207
No problem.

11:18.607 --> 11:19.288
Mr. Shen,

11:19.368 --> 11:21.847
I genuinely admire your work ethic.

11:22.128 --> 11:23.087
Ask anything you need.

11:23.168 --> 11:23.888
I'll cooperate.

11:26.048 --> 11:27.447
Your report to headquarters

11:27.447 --> 11:30.687
stated material and labor cost increases

11:31.128 --> 11:33.447
made the project unprofitable
for the contractor,

11:33.927 --> 11:35.607
leading to his unauthorized loans

11:36.048 --> 11:37.687
and eventual absconding with funds.

11:38.207 --> 11:38.768
Yes.

11:39.248 --> 11:40.567
That's the whole story.

11:41.168 --> 11:44.528
Material and labor costs did rise.

11:45.048 --> 11:48.087
But there is a sequence problem.

11:49.248 --> 11:51.447
Repeated rework delayed our progress,

11:52.248 --> 11:53.567
squandering labor

11:54.288 --> 11:56.008
and materials.

11:56.447 --> 11:57.648
We had to restock

11:58.087 --> 11:59.207
and reconstruct.

11:59.567 --> 12:00.888
Over time,

12:01.528 --> 12:04.528
it resulted in increases
in material and labor costs.

12:10.727 --> 12:14.567
Every rework cycle meant new purchases

12:15.288 --> 12:18.008
and recalculated labor expenses.

12:18.248 --> 12:20.727
There were plenty of opportunities
for manipulation.

12:24.087 --> 12:26.927
In other words, embezzlement.

12:29.488 --> 12:32.447
You're saying the contractors
sabotaged work?

12:34.687 --> 12:36.008
Those scoundrels.

12:37.847 --> 12:39.807
As branch head,

12:40.248 --> 12:43.368
you failed to supervise contractors

12:44.768 --> 12:46.008
and repeatedly pled ignorance.

12:46.648 --> 12:47.888
Mr. Shen,

12:48.248 --> 12:49.607
you don't understand.

12:50.048 --> 12:52.368
After Wu from
Anqiang Construction absconded,

12:53.528 --> 12:54.847
I have been fully occupied.

12:55.288 --> 12:57.327
Hundreds of workers mean
hundreds of mouths to feed.

12:57.447 --> 12:58.687
They need to eat and get paid.

12:58.687 --> 13:00.368
I also need to report back to the group.

13:00.607 --> 13:01.128
I...

13:01.967 --> 13:02.607
Three days.

13:04.648 --> 13:05.687
You have only three days.

13:07.248 --> 13:11.408
From project initiation till now,
all procurement quotes,

13:12.008 --> 13:13.008
actual expenditures,

13:13.567 --> 13:14.528
and employee salaries,

13:14.847 --> 13:15.727
compile them for me.

13:16.008 --> 13:16.727
No way.

13:17.248 --> 13:18.288
Three days aren't enough.

13:18.727 --> 13:19.687
Even a week won't work.

13:20.447 --> 13:21.207
Three days.

13:34.807 --> 13:35.327
Come in.

13:39.087 --> 13:39.768
Mr. Qiu,

13:40.727 --> 13:43.687
I'd like to request
doing a solo live stream.

13:45.368 --> 13:46.168
Are you sure?

13:48.408 --> 13:49.648
Hello, everyone.

13:49.648 --> 13:50.687
Hello.

13:50.687 --> 13:51.327
Hey, everyone.

13:51.327 --> 13:53.327
Welcome to Yan's live stream.

13:53.687 --> 13:56.408
Today, we're still selling
our top-selling product:

13:56.447 --> 13:57.488
boneless chicken feet.

13:57.488 --> 13:58.128
Right.

13:58.327 --> 13:59.327
Today...

13:59.888 --> 14:01.687
(Yes, people are asking
for chicken feet.)

14:01.888 --> 14:02.368
Yes.

14:02.368 --> 14:04.408
Today's deal is even more explosive.

14:04.607 --> 14:06.008
Here's how today's promotion works.

14:06.048 --> 14:08.207
Let me explain
our benefits mechanism, okay?

14:13.008 --> 14:15.528
(For one regular 500g pack
of chicken feet,)

14:15.528 --> 14:18.768
(we'll give you a 250g pack)

14:19.128 --> 14:21.248
(plus another 250g pack.)

14:21.528 --> 14:24.048
(So you get three packs
for the price of one.)

14:24.607 --> 14:25.648
(Buy one, get two free.)

14:25.648 --> 14:26.727
(Buy one, get two free.)

14:26.727 --> 14:28.447
(Today's deal
is incredibly cost-effective.)

14:28.807 --> 14:29.488
- (Right?)
- (Exactly.)

14:31.768 --> 14:33.248
Take a closer look.

14:34.607 --> 14:35.327
141.

14:35.408 --> 14:36.447
141. This isn't right.

14:36.607 --> 14:37.207
This one?

14:37.207 --> 14:38.008
There's an issue.

14:38.008 --> 14:39.087
You need to verify this.

14:39.128 --> 14:39.687
Okay.

14:39.727 --> 14:40.488
Take a look.

14:41.087 --> 14:41.768
You guys check.

14:41.927 --> 14:42.607
No problem.

14:42.607 --> 14:43.368
It's good here.

14:43.408 --> 14:43.967
Look here.

14:44.248 --> 14:44.847
Check here.

14:45.327 --> 14:46.168
You guys continue.

14:46.168 --> 14:47.168
(For Resting)
Okay, you go ahead, Mr. Shen.

14:49.368 --> 14:50.408
What we just reviewed...

14:50.567 --> 14:51.248
Hello, Chen.

14:51.567 --> 14:52.327
Mr. Shen,

14:53.128 --> 14:55.847
there's something you need to check.

14:56.207 --> 14:57.648
I've sent the link to your phone.

14:57.888 --> 14:58.408
Okay.

14:59.852 --> 15:01.351
(Chen Lin: Link)

15:02.607 --> 15:04.048
(We're selling at such a low price.)

15:04.048 --> 15:06.168
(So viewers who love chicken feet,)

15:06.408 --> 15:07.408
(place your orders now.)

15:07.488 --> 15:08.447
(It's delicious.)

15:08.567 --> 15:10.327
(Warm Harbor placed 20 orders!)

15:10.528 --> 15:11.984
(20 orders! Thanks for the support.)

15:13.447 --> 15:14.488
(Thank you, Warm Harbor.)

15:14.528 --> 15:15.888
(Thank you so much.)

15:15.888 --> 15:16.447
(Thank you.)

15:16.447 --> 15:17.927
(You love chicken feet, right?)

15:18.807 --> 15:20.207
(I super like you.)

15:20.288 --> 15:21.368
(Ms. Xu, you're so pretty.)

15:21.368 --> 15:23.567
(Warm Harbor sent a carnival gift.)

15:24.008 --> 15:25.888
(Thanks for the carnival gift,
Warm Harbor.)

15:26.248 --> 15:27.447
(Thanks for liking me.)

15:27.528 --> 15:28.567
(Thank you, Warm Harbor,)

15:28.727 --> 15:29.567
(for supporting me.)

15:29.607 --> 15:31.807
(If I select better products later,)

15:31.847 --> 15:33.168
(I'll share them with you, okay?)

15:33.207 --> 15:34.927
(Thank you, Warm Harbor.)

15:35.087 --> 15:35.807
(Now,)

15:35.847 --> 15:37.687
(we'll continue
selling our hot product:)

15:37.888 --> 15:38.927
(boneless chicken feet.)

15:39.008 --> 15:39.648
(That's right.)

15:41.360 --> 15:43.338
(Do not imitate)

15:43.668 --> 15:45.644
(Confirm order.)

15:45.768 --> 15:47.927
PromiseKeeper placed 50 orders!

15:48.008 --> 15:49.488
(PromiseKeeper: 50 orders)
Thanks for placing 50 orders!

15:50.768 --> 15:52.048
They really love chicken feet.

15:52.048 --> 15:52.528
Exactly.

15:52.607 --> 15:53.207
Right?

15:53.488 --> 15:55.248
Thank you, PromiseKeeper.

15:55.248 --> 15:56.168
(Your chicken feet...)

15:56.168 --> 15:57.888
(Backend team, listen up.)

15:58.128 --> 16:01.207
(For the orders from PromiseKeeper
and Warm Harbor,)

16:01.207 --> 16:01.727
(well,)

16:02.008 --> 16:03.087
(expedite shipping, okay?)

16:03.087 --> 16:03.967
(Copy that. Expedite!)

16:05.248 --> 16:06.768
(Ms. Xu, I bought some too.)

16:06.807 --> 16:07.967
(I like Sichuan cuisine,)

16:08.087 --> 16:09.207
(and I like you more.)

16:09.687 --> 16:10.488
(Thank you.)

16:10.727 --> 16:12.888
Warm Harbor placed 70 orders!

16:13.087 --> 16:14.687
(Thanks for placing 70 orders!)

16:15.008 --> 16:16.128
(Thank you for liking me.)

16:16.168 --> 16:17.248
(Thank you, Warm Harbor,)

16:17.408 --> 16:18.528
(for supporting me.)

16:18.567 --> 16:19.248
(Now,)

16:19.248 --> 16:22.128
(we'll continue selling
our hot product: boneless chicken feet.)

16:22.224 --> 16:22.888
(That's right.)

16:22.888 --> 16:25.248
(PromiseKeeper: 100 orders)
PromiseKeeper placed 100 orders!

16:25.408 --> 16:27.727
(Warm Harbor: 150 orders)
Warm Harbor placed 150 orders!

16:27.888 --> 16:29.488
Thanks for supporting us
with 150 orders!

16:30.567 --> 16:31.648
(Thanks for your support!)

16:32.687 --> 16:33.888
(Thanks for your support!)

16:34.607 --> 16:35.807
Warm Harbor?

16:35.927 --> 16:37.008
It's him again?

16:37.327 --> 16:38.567
All the 50, 70, and 100 orders.

16:38.567 --> 16:40.288
Can they really consume
hundreds of orders?

16:40.607 --> 16:41.368
Is he a wholesaler?

16:42.447 --> 16:44.128
Why care if he's a wholesaler?

16:44.408 --> 16:46.447
This is the biggest spender
from her live stream.

16:46.847 --> 16:48.408
Undoubtedly the top contributor.

16:49.447 --> 16:51.528
Well... Uh...

16:52.207 --> 16:54.128
Do we have enough stock? Check now.

16:54.128 --> 16:55.288
- Check stock.
- Roger that!

16:55.327 --> 16:56.128
If possible,

16:56.168 --> 16:57.927
(Do not imitate)
(expedite shipping for them, okay?)

16:58.128 --> 16:58.847
- (Okay.)
- (Alright.)

16:58.967 --> 16:59.847
(Let's move on.)

16:59.927 --> 17:01.607
(We don't have much stock left.)

17:01.768 --> 17:03.567
Mr. Shen, come here please.

17:03.567 --> 17:04.087
(Thank you.)

17:04.087 --> 17:04.528
(Thanks.)

17:04.607 --> 17:05.607
(Thanks for the support.)

17:05.607 --> 17:06.248
(Thank you.)

17:08.607 --> 17:09.488
That's childish.

17:16.728 --> 17:17.647
Ms. Xu.

17:19.887 --> 17:21.887
I've talked so much my lips are chapped.

17:25.208 --> 17:28.248
Hosting live streams
is like being a celebrity.

17:28.847 --> 17:30.488
You need to pamper and retain your fans.

17:31.087 --> 17:34.607
Warm Harbor's massive orders
in your stream

17:34.688 --> 17:37.167
could stock a small supermarket.

17:37.488 --> 17:39.448
They just want to meet you offline

17:39.528 --> 17:40.847
and have coffee with you.

17:41.167 --> 17:43.607
That's not unreasonable, right?

17:58.048 --> 17:59.208
Understood, Mr. Qiu.

18:00.048 --> 18:00.768
I'll go.

18:01.887 --> 18:02.847
You finally came around.

18:28.528 --> 18:29.887
Excuse me.

18:31.208 --> 18:34.448
Are you Warm Harbor?

18:35.208 --> 18:35.728
No.

18:35.847 --> 18:36.607
Wrong person.

18:37.288 --> 18:38.288
Sorry about that.

18:40.807 --> 18:41.647
Sis-in-law.

18:59.807 --> 19:00.887
Top contributor?

19:03.448 --> 19:04.567
Warm Harbor?

19:05.887 --> 19:07.167
My teacher taught me:

19:07.327 --> 19:08.807
Home is the warm harbor.

19:12.607 --> 19:13.768
Your teacher was right.

19:15.248 --> 19:15.968
Haochen,

19:16.647 --> 19:18.768
where'd you get money
for the stream orders?

19:19.968 --> 19:21.688
I used Ms. Hui's phone.

19:22.847 --> 19:23.688
Ms. Hui,

19:24.127 --> 19:25.127
did you top up?

19:25.887 --> 19:26.807
It's done.

19:27.127 --> 19:27.567
Here.

19:27.567 --> 19:28.127
Thanks.

19:30.367 --> 19:32.127
Can I repay you in cash later?

19:32.288 --> 19:33.008
Okay.

19:33.807 --> 19:35.008
I'm happy to do anything

19:35.048 --> 19:35.768
to help Xu Yan.

19:41.008 --> 19:42.048
What's wrong?

19:42.327 --> 19:44.048
I'll transfer the money to Ms. Hui.

19:44.167 --> 19:45.008
Tell her later...

19:45.327 --> 19:46.367
Don't bother.

19:46.488 --> 19:48.048
I'll repay her with my gift money.

19:48.048 --> 19:48.728
It's done.

19:49.087 --> 19:49.728
Wait.

19:50.768 --> 19:51.567
Shen Haochen,

19:53.887 --> 19:56.728
remember two things from now on.

19:57.807 --> 19:58.448
First,

19:59.248 --> 20:02.367
no more ordering from live streams.

20:02.567 --> 20:03.327
And second?

20:05.847 --> 20:06.488
Second,

20:08.807 --> 20:10.327
remember what I just said.

20:15.367 --> 20:15.968
Wait.

20:17.407 --> 20:18.008
By the way,

20:18.607 --> 20:20.087
all the stuff you bought

20:21.327 --> 20:23.127
wasn't shipped to your home.

20:23.607 --> 20:24.407
Where did it go?

20:25.448 --> 20:27.288
My brother supports an orphanage.

20:27.327 --> 20:28.928
I donated everything there.

20:36.087 --> 20:37.167
You're quite smart.

20:39.448 --> 20:40.688
Not that you did right.

20:44.288 --> 20:45.167
Sis-in-law,

20:45.807 --> 20:47.768
I really miss you.

20:48.008 --> 20:49.528
Mom misses you too.

20:50.248 --> 20:51.968
We've all lost weight lately.

20:52.528 --> 20:54.008
I miss your cooking.

20:57.127 --> 20:58.327
Let me show you something.

21:03.647 --> 21:04.288
Look.

21:05.407 --> 21:07.208
You don't have to move out
for your business.

21:07.567 --> 21:10.048
Look how unhappy my brother is.

21:10.127 --> 21:11.327
He often zones out.

21:17.167 --> 21:17.807
Tell me.

21:17.887 --> 21:19.048
What did my brother do?

21:19.167 --> 21:20.288
I'll have my mom beat him.

21:23.087 --> 21:24.208
No.

21:26.847 --> 21:29.567
Your brother is just overwhelmed
with work.

21:29.847 --> 21:31.488
So don't bother him all the time.

21:31.728 --> 21:32.768
That's not like that.

21:32.768 --> 21:35.688
I can tell he's just missing you.

21:36.127 --> 21:37.208
Can you forgive him

21:37.208 --> 21:38.567
and come home with me?

21:39.887 --> 21:42.248
I'm begging you.

21:50.448 --> 21:51.887
Can't you really come home?

21:57.327 --> 21:58.167
Now look.

21:59.048 --> 22:00.288
Both of you left home.

22:01.448 --> 22:02.768
The house feels completely empty.

22:11.208 --> 22:12.567
Where is your brother?

22:13.167 --> 22:15.248
My dad sent him
to a branch office out of town.

22:15.448 --> 22:16.928
He might not return for months.

22:23.087 --> 22:23.688
Haochen.

22:25.488 --> 22:27.327
Do you remember my phone number?

22:29.607 --> 22:31.048
Call me anytime if you do.

22:31.768 --> 22:32.887
If you miss me,

22:33.208 --> 22:34.087
just call me.

22:34.288 --> 22:35.087
I'll come see you.

22:35.647 --> 22:38.087
We can go wherever you want. Okay?

22:41.167 --> 22:41.928
Really?

22:42.367 --> 22:43.448
Did I ever lie to you?

22:44.327 --> 22:45.327
Promise?

22:45.448 --> 22:46.127
Promise.

22:49.208 --> 22:49.887
Slow down.

22:50.567 --> 22:51.688
I can go anywhere I want?

22:51.807 --> 22:52.807
Anywhere...

22:54.192 --> 22:55.216
Where do you like to go?

22:55.567 --> 22:56.567
I was just saying.

23:09.167 --> 23:09.768
(Is it heavy?)

23:09.928 --> 23:10.448
(Not heavy.)

23:10.968 --> 23:11.928
(Five kilos.)

23:12.607 --> 23:13.607
(Five kilos of water.)

23:13.607 --> 23:14.488
(Five kilos of water.)

23:14.488 --> 23:15.887
(Come on, show our friends.)

23:17.647 --> 23:19.208
(Look, five kilos of water.)

23:19.607 --> 23:20.887
(How's the trash bag quality?)

23:20.968 --> 23:22.288
(Pretty good, right?)

23:22.327 --> 23:23.407
(We're not lying to you.)

23:23.968 --> 23:27.288
(These bags come in extra-thick
and thin versions.)

23:27.488 --> 23:29.528
(But they're equally durable.)

23:30.600 --> 23:32.367
(Braley joined the live stream)

23:32.367 --> 23:33.728
How much for four packs?

23:33.887 --> 23:35.208
9.9 yuan.

23:35.327 --> 23:36.208
Get ready to go on.

23:36.208 --> 23:37.127
Three, two, one.

23:37.127 --> 23:37.887
Attach the link!

23:37.928 --> 23:38.448
(Great.)

23:38.728 --> 23:39.847
(Thank you, guys.)

23:41.008 --> 23:42.288
(She's a notorious gold-digger,)

23:42.688 --> 23:43.807
(trying to marry the rich.)

23:47.728 --> 23:49.647
(That gold-digger streamer)

23:49.688 --> 23:50.887
(wants to marry a rich man.)

23:50.928 --> 23:51.728
(For real?)

23:53.688 --> 23:55.688
Some of you haven't followed yet?

23:55.968 --> 23:57.087
Just touch here to follow.

23:57.167 --> 23:58.008
See it?

23:58.008 --> 23:59.127
Just touch here.

23:59.248 --> 24:01.688
We'll send out a gift next, okay?

24:01.688 --> 24:02.248
Here it is.

24:02.248 --> 24:04.208
Thanks to our new viewers today.

24:04.248 --> 24:05.008
Thank you.

24:05.008 --> 24:06.448
(Got kicked out by the rich family?)

24:07.327 --> 24:08.008
(Interesting.)

24:08.167 --> 24:09.367
(Do a sad housewife act.)

24:09.448 --> 24:10.208
(No need to act.)

24:10.208 --> 24:11.728
(She is already selling trash bags.)

24:11.807 --> 24:12.928
(She is practically sad.)

24:13.008 --> 24:14.607
(She is an abandoned housewife.)

24:19.528 --> 24:21.248
(Why silent? Dance or we cancel orders.)
(Sing, and we'll buy 20.)

24:21.407 --> 24:23.087
(Sing and dance for 30 orders.)

24:23.087 --> 24:25.048
(Get yourself in the bag,
and we'll buy 40.)

24:25.448 --> 24:26.607
(Why isn't she talking?)

24:27.327 --> 24:28.248
(Even got thrown out.)

24:28.248 --> 24:29.327
(Watch your attitude!)

24:29.327 --> 24:30.647
(Dance, or we'll cancel orders.)

24:30.647 --> 24:31.847
(Gold-digger can't handle it.)

24:31.928 --> 24:32.567
(Return!)

24:35.127 --> 24:36.048
(Viewer Analytics)
(How come she's mute?)

24:36.288 --> 24:37.208
(She left.)
(Streamer froze.)

24:37.528 --> 24:38.248
(Gender, Age)
(She is over.)

24:38.367 --> 24:39.327
(Still silent?)

24:39.807 --> 24:40.887
Speak.

24:41.688 --> 24:42.607
Say something.

24:42.847 --> 24:43.607
What's wrong?

24:44.407 --> 24:46.087
Speak!

24:47.248 --> 24:48.087
(No one cheers.)

24:48.087 --> 24:48.528
Speak.

24:55.847 --> 24:57.968
Turn the AC low, please.

24:57.968 --> 24:58.807
It's sweltering.

24:59.607 --> 25:00.208
Got it.

25:00.448 --> 25:01.887
I just saw some viewers asking

25:02.327 --> 25:04.167
if this is big enough to fit a person.

25:04.407 --> 25:06.407
Type one
if you think it can fit someone.

25:06.688 --> 25:08.288
Type two if you disagree. Okay?

25:08.847 --> 25:09.847
Let's test out

25:09.847 --> 25:11.688
if this big trash bag can hold a person.

25:11.887 --> 25:12.847
Luo, help me.

25:13.688 --> 25:14.248
Okay.

25:15.367 --> 25:16.728
(Yes, some are typing one.)

25:16.728 --> 25:17.887
(There's quite a crowd.)

25:18.087 --> 25:19.887
Don't forget to follow us.

25:19.887 --> 25:20.968
Thank you.

25:22.327 --> 25:22.768
Alright.

25:22.768 --> 25:23.647
Let's check it out.

25:25.728 --> 25:28.048
The trash bags are extremely good.

25:28.127 --> 25:29.288
I suggest you

25:29.327 --> 25:30.647
go for the extra-thick version.

25:30.807 --> 25:33.008
(Because the extra-thick ones)

25:33.008 --> 25:34.167
(can handle any weight.)

25:35.008 --> 25:35.928
(Trust me.)

25:36.127 --> 25:36.847
(See?)

25:37.167 --> 25:38.647
(Okay, thanks.)

25:38.768 --> 25:39.688
(Thank you.)

25:39.887 --> 25:40.768
Guess how much damage

25:40.768 --> 25:42.728
you've caused me with this stream?

25:44.607 --> 25:46.928
Ignoring comments counts as an error.

25:47.728 --> 25:49.647
Just standing there for so long!

25:50.008 --> 25:52.127
Is this how you repay my trust?

25:54.167 --> 25:55.127
I'm sorry, Mr. Qiu.

25:55.647 --> 25:56.647
It won't happen again.

25:58.688 --> 26:00.127
And about the follower Warm Harbor,

26:00.847 --> 26:03.448
didn't I tell you to please
and retain any follower?

26:03.728 --> 26:06.167
But you met him offline once

26:06.407 --> 26:07.768
and made his account suspended.

26:08.327 --> 26:09.208
One follower less.

26:11.807 --> 26:12.928
Mr. Qiu, here's the thing.

26:13.567 --> 26:16.127
The person I met was actually a minor

26:16.607 --> 26:18.327
using his parent's phone for shopping.

26:19.208 --> 26:21.087
We can't profit from minors.

26:21.167 --> 26:22.528
So I persuaded him to...

26:23.928 --> 26:24.768
Enough.

26:25.607 --> 26:26.640
You always have reasons.

26:27.280 --> 26:28.784
Don't promote this product anymore.

26:28.928 --> 26:30.887
I'll schedule you
for an outdoor live stream.

26:34.567 --> 26:35.607
I'll do as you say.

26:36.768 --> 26:37.448
Or what?

26:38.448 --> 26:39.688
You're free to leave.

26:40.327 --> 26:41.048
I'll comply.

26:43.167 --> 26:44.807
Just leave if you don't.

26:45.887 --> 26:46.768
Thank you, Mr. Qiu.

26:59.367 --> 27:00.087
Yes.

27:00.327 --> 27:01.407
It's the 5th anniversary.

27:01.528 --> 27:02.367
Yes.

27:02.407 --> 27:03.567
These items are on sale.

27:03.647 --> 27:07.887
Today marks the 5th anniversary

27:08.327 --> 27:09.367
of Daxingfa Supermarket.

27:09.647 --> 27:10.968
That's why we've moved products

27:11.008 --> 27:12.288
to our live stream!

27:12.688 --> 27:13.488
Look at Link 1,

27:13.567 --> 27:14.887
the rapeseed oil.

27:14.928 --> 27:15.728
As I said,

27:15.728 --> 27:16.887
it's non-GMO, cold press,

27:17.008 --> 27:18.528
normally priced at 89.9 yuan.

27:18.528 --> 27:20.248
Today's special, 45.5 yuan!

27:20.248 --> 27:21.127
Get ready to go on.

27:21.127 --> 27:22.008
Three, two, one.

27:22.087 --> 27:23.008
Attach the link!

27:23.008 --> 27:24.167
Listen, guys,

27:24.488 --> 27:26.087
our physical store is located

27:26.087 --> 27:29.288
at Jingzhou Cultural Park.

27:29.448 --> 27:30.928
Jingzhou Cultural Park.

27:31.087 --> 27:32.688
Right next to the ticket booth.

27:32.688 --> 27:35.367
It's crowded here, isn't it?

27:36.127 --> 27:37.248
But online,

27:37.448 --> 27:40.008
we offer the same great deals!

27:42.320 --> 27:43.894
â™ªReady to shineâ™ª

27:44.488 --> 27:45.728
Recently,

27:45.728 --> 27:47.008
Amy has been acting up.

27:47.208 --> 27:47.887
Amy,

27:48.167 --> 27:48.607
be good.

27:48.607 --> 27:49.528
Maybe she's in heat?

27:49.807 --> 27:51.208
Puppies need mates too.

27:51.968 --> 27:52.887
Find her a match.

27:53.008 --> 27:53.528
Sure,

27:53.768 --> 27:54.728
I'll arrange one.

27:55.127 --> 27:55.847
Forget it.

27:56.208 --> 27:59.448
Yan just started Financial News, right?

28:00.208 --> 28:01.327
She was doing well.

28:01.768 --> 28:03.288
Why quit suddenly?

28:04.127 --> 28:06.407
Yan has always been decisive.

28:06.807 --> 28:09.248
She wants to start a business.
Our whole family supports her.

28:11.167 --> 28:12.928
Being a news anchor brings fame

28:12.928 --> 28:13.928
and influence.

28:14.288 --> 28:15.728
Why start up a business?

28:16.167 --> 28:18.048
We've seen enough
struggling entrepreneurs.

28:18.407 --> 28:19.768
Sounds good,

28:19.847 --> 28:21.528
but they have to suffer a lot.

28:22.688 --> 28:24.728
It'll be hard to see Ms. Xu, right?

28:24.928 --> 28:26.488
I'm even starting to miss her.

28:29.087 --> 28:29.807
Ms. Yu.

28:32.367 --> 28:33.127
Ms. Meng.

28:33.488 --> 28:34.248
Ms. Ma.

28:34.528 --> 28:35.288
Ms. Sun.

28:35.367 --> 28:36.127
How are you?

28:36.448 --> 28:36.968
Lei.

28:36.968 --> 28:38.048
What brings you here today?

28:39.528 --> 28:40.847
There's an excellent event.

28:41.327 --> 28:44.008
I'd like to invite you all
to go with me.

29:01.448 --> 29:01.928
Great!

29:03.208 --> 29:03.607
Open.

29:09.887 --> 29:10.647
Awesome!

29:11.647 --> 29:12.327
Impressive!

29:13.008 --> 29:14.087
What is this place?

29:15.728 --> 29:16.528
Why brought us here?

29:16.528 --> 29:17.127
Lei.

29:17.728 --> 29:18.928
Why did you bring us here?

29:18.968 --> 29:20.288
What kind of event could be here?

29:20.807 --> 29:22.127
Let's go check it out.

29:22.887 --> 29:23.728
Why come here?

29:23.968 --> 29:24.688
I don't know.

29:30.488 --> 29:32.008
Restock inventory.

29:32.208 --> 29:33.407
Rapeseed oil. We'll skip this.

29:33.407 --> 29:35.407
Let me show you beef balls, okay?

